name: Alaska Aurora Adventures
description: The Aurora Cabin is a fully furnished log home that is perfect for a Family vacation, or extended stay. The Aurora Cabin was designed for your comfortable stay with large bedrooms with two queen beds per room, comfortable living room, large full bathroom and washer & dryer. Our location is world famous for Northern lights viewing. We offer Arctic circle tours and Dog sledding Being a family ran business our goal is to make your stay relaxing and unforgettable.
